These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, davidoff
There 2 different types of food: apricot, plum
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Cigar   | davidoff    | chaman |
| Food         | plum | apricot    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku
House: colonial, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Hobby   | sudoku | collecting  |
| House     | cape-cod   | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
