The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Flower          | tulip | daffodil |
| Hobby   | gardening   | fishing   |
| Transport     | train       | ship      |

