.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
City: nizza, marseilles
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| City     | marseilles | nizza |
| Cigar   | chaman | prince    |

 #################################

 
