.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, fonseca
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Cigar         | fonseca | bolivar |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| Sport           | baseball          | snowboarding     |

