.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, techno
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade
1. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Flower   | aconite | orchid |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | techno  |
| Beverage     | lemonade | milk    |

 